{"tid":1604324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵有狗查人 點算？","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:25.000Z","uid":316013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a91b3f03a326f81feade19bcfee622543a86a6b","tid":1604324,"uid":316013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"不時見到有Post報黨鐵有十零隻狗查人，令手足唔敢帶gear，或者降低左一般和理非出門意慾。<br />\n<br />\n目標：驅散企係黨鐵站崗嘅狗<br />\n（一般只有十零隻狗）<br />\n方法：遊行集會從自己區出發嘅時候，係黨鐵附近聚集，聚夠一定人數街坊屌狗屌走佢地。狗們會驚你人群聚集會衝擊佢地，佢地基於自身安全就會收隊/鼠入狗鐵控制室。<br />\n<br />\n困難：手足要提早半至一個鐘出門⋯⋯又要訓少陣。"},{"pid":"384263aa02ea6a615043346750f14b34a64fcf49","tid":1604324,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:10:16.000Z","msg":"所以先要分六區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb2f1b0a952a8bbdb1b3c0504a4a0d332d06670","tid":1604324,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U7M7pKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7M7pKH.jpg&h=7377d3c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解有啲人仲可以甘心每日都搭黨鐵？</span></span>"}]}